if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('base_supplier')
and type = 'U')
drop table base_supplier
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: base_supplier */
/*==============================================================*/
create table base_supplier (
supp_id int identity,
supp_code varchar(200) not null,
purc_sourceid int not null,
purc_mode int not null,
supp_name varchar(200) not null,
supp_url varchar(500) not null,
purc_priority tinyint null,
is_grade bit null,
create_time datetime not null default getdate(),
create_user_id bigint not null,
edit_time datetime not null default getdate(),
edit_user_id bigint not null,
del_flag bit not null default 1,
del_time datetime null,
del_user_id bigint null,
remark nvarchar(255) null,
constraint PK_BASE_SUPPLIER primary key (supp_id)
)
go
